    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rabbit Rush</strong> 是一款快速而紧张的动作游戏，玩家控制一只敏捷且坚定的兔子，必须在短短10秒内完成每个关卡。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290030/extras/4a3cd44b8fc33f7f77b92c9467f48747.poster.avif?t=1767979099\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290030/extras/4a3cd44b8fc33f7f77b92c9467f48747.webm?t=1767979099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290030/extras/4a3cd44b8fc33f7f77b92c9467f48747.mp4?t=1767979099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br>目标是在有限的时间内消灭所有敌人，这需要玩家快速反应和精准的策略。每个关卡都带来了新的挑战，敌人种类繁多，还有各种障碍物让这场与时间的赛跑更加困难。凭借复古风格的美术设计、简单的控制和快节奏的音乐，<strong>Rabbit Rush</strong> 提供了一种紧张而激烈的游戏体验，精准操作是取得胜利的关键。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290030/extras/bae79d77b683303eb65be73394123513.poster.avif?t=1767979099\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290030/extras/bae79d77b683303eb65be73394123513.webm?t=1767979099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290030/extras/bae79d77b683303eb65be73394123513.mp4?t=1767979099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特点：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3个不同的世界可供探索</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30个完全独特的关卡等待完成</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着进展出现新敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一把锋利的苦无，或者更确切地说……一根锋利的胡萝卜！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290030/extras/b42227255b9013739d6a5c67551c6f4d.poster.avif?t=1767979099\" width=800 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290030/extras/b42227255b9013739d6a5c67551c6f4d.webm?t=1767979099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290030/extras/b42227255b9013739d6a5c67551c6f4d.mp4?t=1767979099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
